Symbol : CONFIG_NAMESPACES 

Choice : Excluded

Info   : Include network namespace if you are using systemd.

Include PID, NETWORK, IPC namespaces if you are using gentoo.

If you are using Linux containers such as Docker, all options should be enabled.

Otherwise all can be excluded. To know more about namespaces and their uses, follow the link below- 

